This is a directory which stores all the progress evidence documentation of our group.
You could see our two product backlogs (due to requirement change in week 4) and four sprint backlogs (due to 4 sprints in this class) there.
You could also find our individual contribution file which document what we have done everyday there. These files could help you know the contribution of everyone better.
You could also find our communication screenshots on teams almost everyday. Although we are not used to use Microsoft Teams as our mean of communication, we try to demonstrate our communication process.
Happy developer, happy client, perfect product quality is our goal
